item.title: Prayer bpn4923 in Vanuatu
item.description: O God blong mi, God we i givimaot ol samting long yumi mo i gat bigfala sori long yumi. Yu Yu olsem wan king we i mekem olgeta samting i gat laef. Mo Yu Yu no save finis blong givimaot ol paoa mo lav, mo blong soemaot ol gudfala samting blong Yu, nating ol man i traem blokim Yu. Mi prei long Yu blong Yu letem man ia i kasem ol samting we oli save sevem hem long evri wol long ol wol blong Yu.
